Welcome to the Library of Congress.

00:00:27.570 --> 00:00:29.120
I'm John Cole.

00:00:29.120 --> 00:00:32.780
I'm the director of the Center
for the Book at the library,

00:00:32.780 --> 00:00:36.950
which is the reading and
literacy promotion arm.

00:00:36.950 --> 00:00:41.770
We're very pleased to have you
here for one of our noontime talks.

00:00:41.770 --> 00:00:45.470
The Center for the Book itself
was created long time ago

00:00:45.470 --> 00:00:48.860
by Daniel Boorstin when he
was Librarian of Congress.

00:00:48.860 --> 00:00:51.860
