and the technology of television,

00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:13.000
and we very quickly moved into the
business of using new technologies

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:16.780
to promote books and reading
with our first project,

00:01:16.780 --> 00:01:21.350 position:56%
a something called "read more about
it" that people my age will remember

00:01:21.350 --> 00:01:24.920
on CBS television when for
a year, more than a year,

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:27.510
the star of the program
came out and said,

00:01:27.510 --> 00:01:30.390
"if you enjoyed the program
the library suggests,

00:01:30.390 --> 00:01:33.020
