Library of Congress [laughter].

00:01:41.610 --> 00:01:46.490
But the positive message, we're
promoting bookstores and libraries.

00:01:46.490 --> 00:01:49.640
We also are involved with
some national events went

00:01:49.640 --> 00:01:50.940
