00:05:40.030 --> 00:05:43.350
at the Smithsonian
Institution shortly

00:05:43.350 --> 00:05:47.520
after the Smithsonian
was, was created.

00:05:47.520 --> 00:05:50.210
That's only a small part
of the story however.

00:05:50.210 --> 00:05:55.580
That obviously didn't happen,
