00:06:08.920 --> 00:06:12.420
of American History since 1983.

00:06:12.420 --> 00:06:14.510
She's organized many exhibitions.

00:06:14.510 --> 00:06:17.890
I'm not going to talk about
her several publications.

00:06:17.890 --> 00:06:21.850
One of the exhibitions was on
Audubon and the Smithsonian

00:06:21.850 --> 00:06:24.670
for the Smithsonian libraries.

00:06:24.670 --> 00:06:31.790
She also has done research and work
on Kallitype printing, papermaking,

00:06:31.790 --> 00:06:35.600 position:56%
and the history of print collecting,
